FBIS4-32228 "dreeu120_i_94012" FBIS-EEU-94-120 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Exchange Agreed To Aid Search for Dead, Missing Exchange Agreed To Aid Search for Dead, Missing LD2106213594 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 2000 GMT 21 Jun 94 LD2106213594 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] Representatives of the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army and the Croatian Defense Council [HVO] have met in Mostar. They agreed to allow up to 200 people cross from the Muslim to the Croat bank of the Neretva. Each side will try to locate the bodies of dead and missing persons, and reports will be drawn up to this effect at places where prisons and unmarked graves are still believed to exist.
